ghostPage.title: Example Client for Developers
ghostPage.excerpt:
What is the Example Client?
Using the DSNP SDK, the Example Client demonstrates how to quickly integrate
with the DSNP. It is a social app that creates a user identity, posts, replies,
and connections on the social graph. Clone the Example Client and start
developing.

Please note that the Example Client is an example only and not meant for
production applications.
